   title AS t
WHERE lt.id = ml.link_type_id

AND cct1.kind IN ('crew', 'crew', 'crew', 'crew', 'crew')
AND cct2.kind = 'complete'
AND cn.country_code != '[uz]'
AND (cn.name LIKE '%Classplay%' OR cn.name LIKE '%Video%')
